article.headline: Allen, Tezeno lift Southern over Florida A&M 58-44
article.description: — Dreshawn Allen 14 points, Derrick Tezeno added a double-double and Southern defeated Florida A&M 58-44 on Monday night.
article.linkText: Allen, Tezeno lift Southern over Florida A&M 58-44
article.story: BATON ROUGE, La. -- — Dreshawn Allen 14 points, Derrick Tezeno added a double-double and Southern defeated Florida A&M 58-44 on Monday night. Allen shot 5 for 10, including 4 for 5 from beyond the arc for the Jaguars (17-12, 11-5 Southwestern Athletic Conference). Tezeno finished with 13 points and 10 rebounds. Keith Lamar and Jalen Speer scored 14 apiece to lead the Rattlers (6-22, 4-13). Lamar added seven rebounds and two steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
